    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and is best suited for someone looking for a dependable commuter at an affordable price. Mechanically, it runs well, but the exterior does show signs of its age, including several noticeable scratches on the passenger side doors and a few small dings on the hood. Inside, the upholstery is intact but shows some staining and general wear from regular use. It has been a reliable car for us, and with a little bit of cosmetic attention, it still has plenty of life left in it.",
      "price": 20500.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
